      "date": "2013-01-18 18:30:45.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/26b166ac-619d-11e2-b5e0-52540035b04c).  Ran 1 tests.  1 tests failed: node-provisioning-1.",
