          "date": "2013-01-17 03:35:46.000000000",
          "tz": -480
        },
        "subject": "LU-2484 mdt: Remove unused md_stats",
        "message": "LU-2484 mdt: Remove unused md_stats\n\nDo not allocate md_stats for mdt devices since they do not implement\nmd_ops.  Use obd and custom MDT_LPROC_XXX stats rather than ptlrpc\nstats to back /proc/.../mdt/.../stats as the other target classes do.\nAnd add a compatibility symlink from md_stats to stats.\n\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <jhammond@tacc.utexas.edu>\nChange-Id: Ibf2289cdeb477161a3e2478aaffad43c985c22ea\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
